<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Dashboard — Line Engine</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design.css">
    {{#autoRefresh}}<meta http-equiv="refresh" content="{{autoRefreshIntervalSeconds}}">{{/autoRefresh}}
</head>
<body>
{{> _nav }}

<div class="swe-container" style="padding-top: var(--space-xxl); padding-bottom: var(--space-section);">

    <div class="swe-flex-between swe-mb-xl">
        <div>
            <h1 class="swe-display-lg" style="margin: 0;">Dashboard</h1>
            <p class="swe-body-md swe-mute" style="margin: var(--space-sm) 0 0;">
                라인 인스턴스 모니터링 + 재개{{#autoRefresh}} · <span style="color: var(--accent-green);">⟳ Auto-refresh: {{autoRefreshIntervalSeconds}}s</span>{{/autoRefresh}}
            </p>
        </div>
        {{#autoRefresh}}<a href="/line/dashboard" class="swe-btn-tertiary">■ Stop auto</a>{{/autoRefresh}}
        {{^autoRefresh}}<a href="/line/dashboard?auto=1" class="swe-btn-tertiary">↻ Auto-refresh</a>{{/autoRefresh}}
    </div>

    <!-- 통계 (#195 — 글로벌 카운트, 필터와 무관) -->
    <p class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);">
        헤더 카드는 <strong>전체 기간</strong> 기준 · 아래 테이블은 적용된 필터 결과
    </p>
    <div class="swe-grid swe-grid-4 swe-mb-xl">
        <div class="swe-stat-card">
            <div class="swe-stat-label">Total</div>
            <div class="swe-stat-value">{{totalCount}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swe-stat-card">
            <div class="swe-stat-label" style="color: var(--accent-yellow);">Running</div>
            <div class="swe-stat-value">{{runningCount}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swe-stat-card">
            <div class="swe-stat-label" style="color: var(--accent-green);">Completed</div>
            <div class="swe-stat-value">{{completedCount}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="swe-stat-card">
            <div class="swe-stat-label" style="color: var(--accent-red);">Failed</div>
            <div class="swe-stat-value">{{failedCount}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 검색/필터 (#137 — More filters 펼치기) -->
    <div class="swe-card-elevated swe-mb-xl">
        <form method="get" action="/line/dashboard">
            <div class="swe-grid swe-grid-3">
                <div>
                    <label for="workflowName">Line Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="workflowName" name="workflowName" class="swe-input"
                           value="{{#workflowName}}{{workflowName}}{{/workflowName}}" placeholder="Name substring">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label for="instanceId">Instance ID</label>
                    <input type="text" id="instanceId" name="instanceId" class="swe-input"
                           value="{{#instanceId}}{{instanceId}}{{/instanceId}}" placeholder="UUID substring">
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: end; gap: var(--space-md); justify-content: flex-end;">
                    <a href="/line/dashboard" class="swe-btn-secondary">Reset</a>
                    <button type="submit" class="swe-btn-primary">Apply</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <details {{#advancedOpen}}open{{/advancedOpen}} style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
                <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; user-select: none;">More filters</summary>
                <div style="margin-top: var(--space-md); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-md);">
                    <div>
                        <label style="display:block; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); font-weight: 600;">Status (다중 선택 — 모두 미체크 = 전부 표시)</label>
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); flex-wrap: wrap;">
                            <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap: var(--space-xs); cursor: pointer;">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="statusSt" value="RUNNING" {{#selectedRunning}}checked{{/selectedRunning}}>
                                <span class="swe-badge swe-badge-warning">RUNNING</span>
                            </label>
                            <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap: var(--space-xs); cursor: pointer;">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="statusSt" value="COMPLETED" {{#selectedCompleted}}checked{{/selectedCompleted}}>
                                <span class="swe-badge swe-badge-success">COMPLETED</span>
                            </label>
                            <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap: var(--space-xs); cursor: pointer;">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="statusSt" value="FAILED" {{#selectedFailed}}checked{{/selectedFailed}}>
                                <span class="swe-badge swe-badge-danger">FAILED</span>
                            </label>
                            <label style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap: var(--space-xs); cursor: pointer;">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="statusSt" value="TERMINATED" {{#selectedTerminated}}checked{{/selectedTerminated}}>
                                <span class="swe-badge swe-badge-secondary">TERMINATED</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swe-grid swe-grid-2" style="gap: var(--space-md);">
                        <div>
                            <label for="startDtFrom">시작일 from</label>
                            <input type="date" id="startDtFrom" name="startDtFrom" class="swe-input"
                                   value="{{startDtFrom}}">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label for="startDtTo">시작일 to</label>
                            <input type="date" id="startDtTo" name="startDtTo" class="swe-input"
                                   value="{{startDtTo}}">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 11px;">
                        날짜 범위는 <code>START_DT</code> 기준 inclusive 양 끝 (to는 23:59:59까지 포함).
                        정렬은 컬럼 헤더 클릭으로 변경 (시작/종료/등록일).
                        {{#appliedDateDefault}}<br>💡 첫 진입 — <strong>최근 7일</strong> 기본 적용 중. 다른 기간 보려면 위 입력 수정 후 Apply.{{/appliedDateDefault}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </details>
            <!-- 정렬 키 hidden — 헤더 클릭으로만 변경 -->
            <input type="hidden" name="sortBy" value="{{sortBy}}">
            <input type="hidden" name="sortDir" value="{{sortDir}}">
        </form>
    </div>

    <!-- 인스턴스 테이블 -->
    <div class="swe-card" style="padding: 0;">
        <table class="swe-table">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>ID</th>
                <th>Line</th>
                <th>Status</th>
                <th>
                    <a href="{{{startDtSortHref}}}" class="swe-mute" style="text-decoration: none;">
                        Started {{#sortStartDt}}{{#sortAsc}}▲{{/sortAsc}}{{^sortAsc}}▼{{/sortAsc}}{{/sortStartDt}}
                    </a>
                </th>
                <th>
                    <a href="{{{endDtSortHref}}}" class="swe-mute" style="text-decoration: none;">
                        Ended {{#sortEndDt}}{{#sortAsc}}▲{{/sortAsc}}{{^sortAsc}}▼{{/sortAsc}}{{/sortEndDt}}
                    </a>
                </th>
                <th class="swe-text-right">Action</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            {{#instances}}
            <tr>
                <td class="swe-id-cell" title="{{id}}">{{id}}</td>
                <td>{{workflowName}}</td>
                <td>
                    <span class="swe-badge swe-badge-{{badgeClass}}">{{statusSt}}</span>
                </td>
                <td class="swe-mute">{{startDt}}</td>
                <td class="swe-mute">{{#endDt}}{{endDt}}{{/endDt}}{{^endDt}}—{{/endDt}}</td>
                <td class="swe-actions">
                    <a href="/line/instance/{{id}}" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">Details</a>
                </td>
            </tr>
            {{/instances}}
            {{^instances}}
            <tr>
                <td colspan="6" style="text-align: center; padding: var(--space-section) 0; color: var(--mute);">
                    {{#filterEmptyDiagnostic}}
                    <!-- #195 진단형 empty state — 헤더엔 totalCount건 있으나 현재 필터로 0건일 때 -->
                    <div style="max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto;">
                        <div class="swe-ink" style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">
                            전체 <strong>{{totalCount}}</strong>건 중 현재 필터에 해당하는 인스턴스가 <strong>0건</strong>입니다.
                        </div>
                        <div style="font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); line-height: 1.7;">
                            현재 필터 — 기간 <code>{{startDtFrom}}</code> ~ <code>{{startDtTo}}</code>
                            · status <code>{{appliedStatusLabel}}</code>
                            {{#workflowName}} · Line name <code>{{workflowName}}</code>{{/workflowName}}
                            {{#instanceId}} · Instance ID <code>{{instanceId}}</code>{{/instanceId}}
                        </div>
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-sm); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                            <a href="/line/dashboard" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">필터 초기화 (최근 7일)</a>
                            <a href="{{quickLinkBroader}}" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">최근 {{quickLinkBroaderDays}}일 보기</a>
                            <a href="{{quickLinkAllTime}}" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">전체 기간 보기</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="swe-mute" style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: var(--space-md);">
                            여전히 0건이라면 ACL 가시성(라인 권한) 또는 시드 데이터의 startDt 분포를 확인하세요.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {{/filterEmptyDiagnostic}}
                    {{^filterEmptyDiagnostic}}
                    <!-- 진짜 데이터 없음 — 헤더 통계도 0 -->
                    No instances. Use <a href="/line/schedules" class="swe-ink">Schedules</a> to create one.
                    {{/filterEmptyDiagnostic}}
                </td>
            </tr>
            {{/instances}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        {{> _pagination }}
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
